700743f-b.title: Bronx: City Island Avenue - Marine Street
700743f-b.text:
88 City Island Avenue (City lIsland); at the S.E. corner
of Marine Street, showing the Upper Bronx Community Center. The
City Island branch office of the Western Union Telegraph Company
is also lOCated here.
Summer, 1923
P. L. Sperr
NO RPRODUTTIONS
(2)
The same, at a later dute. The Marine Restaurant occupies
the house.
July 6, 1936
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
